languages.text: "Гадкий старикашка!" {n}Винтерскейл яростно мотает головой, стараясь сбросить псайкерское наваждение. Когда ваши взгляды вновь пересекаются, осознание вдруг отпечатывается на его лице.{/n} "Надо же... {mf|новенький|новенькая}! Вот это встреча! Что ты забыл{mf||а} на моем мире?"

traits.locale_text: "Гадкий старикашка!" {n}Винтерскейл яростно мотает головой, стараясь сбросить псайкерское навождение. Когда ваши взгляды вновь пересекаются, осознание вдруг отпечатывается на его лице.{/n} "Надо же... {mf|новенький|новенькая}! Вот это встреча! Что ты забыл{mf||а} на моем мире?"

languages.text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

traits.locale_text: "Loathsome old man!" {n}Winterscale angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition blooms on his face.{/n} "What a surprise, new blood! What an encounter! What did you forget on my world?"

languages.text: «¡Viejo despreciable!». {n}Winterscale menea furiosamente la cabeza, tratando de sacudirse los efectos del conjuro del psíquico. Cuando vuestras miradas se cruzan de nuevo, una expresión de reconocimiento aflora en su rostro.{/n} «¡Qué sorpresa, {mf|novato|novata}! ¡Qué encuentro tan fortuito! ¿Qué hace en mi planeta?».
languages.original_text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

Cuando vuestras miradas se cruzan de nuevo, una expresión de reconocimiento aflora a su rostro.{/n} «¡Qué sorpresa, {mf|novato|novata}! ¡Qué encuentro tan fortuito! ¿Qué se le ha perdido en mi planeta?».

languages.text: “该死的老树杈！”{n}卡里戈斯愤怒地摇了摇头，试图摆脱这个灵能者的咒语。当你们的目光再次相遇时，他脸上露出了恍然大悟的神情。{/n}“是你吗，新来的？没想到会在这种地方遇到你！你怎么会跑到我的世界来？”
languages.original_text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

traits.locale_text: “该死的老家伙！”{n}温特斯凯尔愤怒地摇了摇头，试图摆脱这个灵能者的咒语。当你们的目光再次相遇时，他脸上露出了恍然大悟的神情。{/n}“真是令人惊讶，新来的！没想到会在这里遇到你！莫非你在我的世界里落下了什么东西吗？”

languages.text: « Maudit vieillard ! » {n}Calligos secoue la tête d'un air furieux en essayant de lutter contre le sortilège du psyker. Quand vos regards se croisent à nouveau, vous voyez qu'il vous reconnaît.{/n} « C'est vous, novice ? Quelle surprise ! Que venez-vous faire sur mon monde ? »
languages.original_text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

languages.text: 「憎らしい老いぼれめ！」{n}カリゴスは怒って頭を振り、異能者の呪文を振り払おうとする。再び視線が合うと、彼の顔に知った相手を見た輝きが宿る。{/n}「お前なのか、新米よ！まさかここで出会うとはな！俺の世界で一体何をしている？」
languages.original_text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

languages.text: "Schändlicher alter Zweig!" {n}Calligos schüttelt zornig den Kopf, um den Zauber des Psionikers abzuschütteln. Als Eure Blicke sich erneut begegnen, scheint er dich endlich zu erkennen.{/n} "Seid Ihr das, neues Blut? Euch hätte ich hier nicht erwartet. Was in der Leere macht Ihr in meiner Welt?"
languages.original_text: "Loathsome old twig!" {n}Calligos angrily shakes his head, trying to throw off the psyker's spell. When your gazes meet again, recognition dawns on his face.{/n} "Is that you, new blood? Fancy meeting you here! What in the void are you doing on my world?"

traits.locale_text: "Schändlicher alter Mann!" {n}Winterzunder schüttelt zornig den Kopf, um den psionischen Zauber abzuschütteln. Als Eure Blicke sich begegnen, erkennt er dich langsam und sein Gesicht leuchtet auf.{/n} "So eine Überraschung, neues Blut! Was für eine Begegnung! Was habt Ihr in meiner Welt vergessen?"

languages.text: "İğrenç, sıska ihtiyar seni!" {n}Calligos, ruhsezerin büyüsünden kurtulmaya çalışarak öfkeyle kafasını sallıyor. Göz göze geldiğinizde yüzünde seni tanıdığına dair bir ifade beliriyor.{/n} "Seni mi görüyorum taze kan? Seni burada göreceğim hayatta aklıma gelmezdi! Uçsuz alsın seni, dünyamda ne işin var?"
